{% comment %}
  Mmm! — DSHEA disclaimer partial. COMPLIANCE-CRITICAL (build principle #5).

  Must render on: every PDP, the quiz result, cart/checkout upsell surfaces,
  and every email footer (Klaviyo carries its own copy of this string —
  keep them identical).

  Usage:
    {% render 'mmm-disclaimer' %}
    {% render 'mmm-disclaimer', provider_note: true %}   <- adds the provider line;
       required on every recommendation surface (quiz result, personalized PDP blocks).

  Do not shrink below .mmm-fine-print size, hide behind a toggle, or lighten
  the color past --mmm-ink-soft. Visible means visible.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="mmm-fine-print mmm-disclaimer" data-mmm-disclaimer>
  <p>
    These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration.
    This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
  </p>
  {%- if provider_note -%}
    <p>
      Mmm! is not a substitute for professional advice. Talk to your provider if
      you&rsquo;re pregnant, on medication, or managing a condition.
    </p>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>
